Package: oyranos-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends: oyranos (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: Color Management System Development Files
 The library allows one to match predictably input device colours to 
 output device colours across supporting applications. One goal 
 is to make colour management useful for all users in a automated 
 fashion and regardless of any technical knowledge.
 Headers and development files for Oyranos.

